'''2,2'-联吡啶'''是[[联吡啶|联吡啶]]异构体之一，无色固体。它是一个[[双齿|双齿]][[螯合|螯合]][[配体_(化学)|配体]]，可以和很多金属离子形成[[配合物|配合物]]，因此可作[[氧化还原指示剂|氧化还原指示剂]]。与[[钌|钌]]和[[铂|铂]]的配合物具有很强的发光性质，可能有潜在应用。

bipy及其衍生物<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Smith, A. P.; Lamba, J. J. S.; Fraser, C. L. | title = Efficient Synthesis of Halomethyl-2,2'-Bipyridines: 4,4'-Bis(chloromethyl)-2,2'-Bipyridine | collvol = 10 | collvolpages = 107 | year = 2004 | prep = v78p0082}}</ref><ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Smith, A. P.; Savage, S. A.; Love, J.; Fraser, C. L. | title = Synthesis of 4-, 5-, and 6-Methyl-2,2'-Bipyridine by a Negishi Cross-Coupling Strategy | collvol = 10 | collvolpages = 517 | year = 2004 | prep = v78p0051}}</ref> 可通过[[吡啶|吡啶]]与[[雷尼镍|雷尼镍]]作用[[脱氢|脱氢]]得到。<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = Sasse, W. H. F. | title = 2,2’-Bipyridine | collvol = 5 | collvolpages = 102 | year = 1973 | prep = cv5p0102}}</ref> 常见的2,2'-联吡啶配合物包括：
*Mo(CO)<sub>4</sub>(bipy)，类似[[六羰基钼|Mo(CO)<sub>6</sub>]]；
*RuCl<sub>2</sub>(bipy)<sub>2</sub>，合成前体；<ref>{{cite journal | author = Lay, P. A.; Sargeson, A. M.; [[Henry_Taube|Taube, H.]] | title = cis-Bis(2,2’-Bipyridine-N,N’) Complexes of Ruthenium(III)/(II) and Osmium(III)/(II) | journal = [[Inorg._Synth.|Inorg. Synth.]] | year = 1986 | volume = 24 | pages = 291–299 | doi = 10.1002/9780470132555.ch78}}</ref>
*[[三(2,2'-联吡啶)氯化钌|[Ru(bipy)<sub>3</sub>]Cl<sub>2</sub>]]，常用的发光物质；
*[Fe(bipy)<sub>3</sub>]<sup>2+</sup>，用于亚铁离子的[[比色|比色]]分析。

